comments.body:
Would it make sense to also reset `connman` here as is done in [process_message.cpp](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/da769855d0ce60c4a5ded844a4d4c43917a6e027/src/test/fuzz/process_message.cpp?#L75) and [process_messages.cpp](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/da769855d0ce60c4a5ded844a4d4c43917a6e027/src/test/fuzz/process_messages.cpp?#L65)?

```suggestion
    auto& connman{static_cast<ConnmanTestMsg&>(*node.connman)};
    connman.Reset();
```

